  "name": "Classify resume with ai from Resume email and send to Google Sheets",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: Classify resume with ai from Resume email and send to Google Sheets",
  "category": "AI",
  "tags": [
